Use the standard library
This is how to largest_divisor of n:
   Remember that d is diff of n and 1
   Do this d times:
      When remainder of n and d is 0, then:
         The answer is d
      End when
      Decrease d
   End do
   The answer is 1
Now you know
>>> largest_divisor of 15
5
>>> largest_divisor of 3
1
>>> largest_divisor of 7
1